rows.label: qst200304_msg0001
rows.name: I think I'm all right...just about.

rows.label: qst200304_msg0002
rows.name:
If it weren't for that big Blade, though,
I'd have been a goner.

rows.label: qst200304_msg0004
rows.name:
I can't believe a Gogol caused
this whole mess...

rows.label: qst200304_msg0005
rows.name:
I hope you'll find that thing and make
sure it doesn't hurt anyone again.
